BR_text.BRsummary: Deleting last remaining Execution in ExecutionIndex throws an error
BR_text.BRdescription:
Deleting the last remaining execution from the execution index throws an error as shown below:
 <denchmark-link:https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/11476842/76121868-51412100-5fba-11ea-9e9a-4c9f72a6a514.png></denchmark-link>
 
 This is most probably because, on deleting the execution, both
 <denchmark-code>this.$table.on('click', '.exec-row', event => this.onExecutionClicked(event));
 this.$table.on('click', '.delete-exec', event => this.onExecutionDelete(event));
 </denchmark-code>
 
 events are called.
